Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:49.11,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Burn bright like a true champion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:53.20,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1.5}kyojin no hoshi wo tsukamu made
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:53.20,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}until the Star of the Giants is in your hands!
