Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:29.99,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs110\blur1\c&H2B28CA&\pos(952,730)}Shine on! Star of the Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Giants aren't budging an inch! {gekitou ni -- rikitou no, kyoujin hoshi-doushi}{Yume alt:The Giants are going all out!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And standing front and center is Hoshi Hyuuma, who just isn't letting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, his magic ball, the Big League Ball 3, seems to be losing its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect game is still possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Hoshi!\N You can't throw any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Hoshi! \NYour body won't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike! Batter out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go for\N the perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more! One more and the\N Giants will have a perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one... just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Giants want\N their perfect game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll have to get through the\N Chuunichi Dragons' final pinch hitter.{used the team's full name FYI}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than Ban Chuuta,\N Hoshi Hyuuma's former best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The star I've been \Nchasing this whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the great Star of the Giants,\N is shining before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and with \Nthis left hand of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With this left hand, \NI'll make that star mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this, \N just swing the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you hold that handstand to push you to your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{ 奇天烈 }I know Coach has a reason behind\N this weird plan of his, but dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole body hurts!\N I can barely see straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I even hit that\N pitch of his like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma, your left arm... it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this, Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... my vision's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one strike\N from Big League Ball 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two more strikes to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban, keep your eyes forward!\N That throw was weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can barely feel my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes another\N Big League Ball 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi is showing some fatigue in\N this face-off against the final batter. {asssuming  疲労?} {S: aye}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's thrown his third ball!\N It's another Big League Ball 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ball's \Nway off its mark! {tlc?}{good enough, "ball wa gaikaku ni ookiku hazuremashita"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hoshi gets hurt, baseball \Nas we know it will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I just have to get to \Nthe grounds as soon as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,1-2! {1 str. 2 ball}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... just holding the bat is enough to make me feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two more strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is falling apart\N before my very eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure you've got\N it much worse than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{sono kagirenai kutsuu ga perfect no eikou ni yotte mukuwareru koto inoru}I hope this endless pain you're suffering through gets you a perfect game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please win, Hoshi.\N Please win, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have taken\N quite a turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect game is right under his nose, but Hoshi's starting to lose his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If he throws another ball, all the \Nwork they've put in will go up in smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{疲労困憊}And Ban Chuuta is exhausted\N after Coach Hoshi's strange plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{S: However, it is now clear that Hyuuma Hoshi is on the verge of exhaustion as well (after giving it his best until now).}However, Hoshi Hyuuma is also on the verge of collapse after a tough game. {dc: kinda liberal, but i feel this is more sports-announcer-y}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi, \Nget it together, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two more throws!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi,\N what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong,\N everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hoshi? Why're\N you struggling against a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi, don't worry.\N Just give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be here,\N backing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{not sure of word after "sono"} {S: ギョロ目?  // Hey, An-chan, make sure you have your eyes peeled on my winning throw, alright?  // which further justifies line 92?}Hey, keep your eyes \Npeeled for the winning ball.{also, avoiding "an-chan" incase it's short for "aniki" or something cringe like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chou, as long as you don't do one of your signature slip-ups, we're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you've said it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where\N it flies, I'll catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So send 'em my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hoshi, leave\N the winning ball to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just got one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mori, it's all you.{just check if I've got his name right <_<} {S: yeah}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi, as your catcher, \Nyou could at least tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been ignoring my signs and throwing weak pitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you been\N throwing any strikes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't know \Nwhat he's got up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got me on edge.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They've seen through\N Big League Ball 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,While I don't have \Ntime to go into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,think about all those who\N have hit Big League Ball 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako from the Hanshin Tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramatsu from the Taiyo Whales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi from the Hiroshima Carps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All pitchers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Big League Ball 3's fatal flaw \Nis the slow swing of a pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぼくはその敵に対してストライクゾーンギリギリにはずれた臭い球を投げることによって切り抜けて来ました}I was only able to take them out with\N weak balls on the edge of the strike zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Hoshi made Ban hold a \Nhandstand to dull his senses and swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to settle this\N with a decisive pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The pitcher's after a perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not gonna \Nthrow another ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be throwing for a strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let this chance get away!\N Keep your eyes on it and swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball... pass me the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball... give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just skims third base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Foul! Foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect game\N was almost lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream continues,\N but it was a close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fierce stand-off has \Nme on the edge of my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's currently 2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The last pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the grand finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They know this pitch\N decides everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be a perfect game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will Chuunichi's \NBan stand in his way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the last pitch can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one... just one more pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fated pitch is upon us.\N Will Hoshi get his perfect game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back at it \Nafter a long pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you\N think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ticket! \NShow me your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi hasn't moved an inch,\N eyes fixed on his former friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All 50,000 spectators in the stadium have held their breath and can't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's hearts are beating in unison \Nwith Hoshi, like we've all become one being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi has raised his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi has his left \Nfoot on the plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He begins his motions\N of the final pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hoshi swings both his hands back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi, you have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lifts up his leg \Nand pulls his left arm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he finish it with\N a Big League Ball 3?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Somebody! Somebody stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi lowers his arm and sends \Nthe pitch towards the home plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And there it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it, Ban! Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And he hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes to left of center field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going with some force!\N Will it break through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Left fielder is \Nmaking a run for it! {sounds like he says his name?   S: Takada, but you probably don't need it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And so goes the center!  {S: just in case, this guy is Shibata}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not slowing down! {S: or be more precise, it's not touching the ground/not falling down}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this game be perfect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And it goes through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball's rolling \Ntowards the outer fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes the\N perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinch hitter, Ban Chuuta, gets a perfect hit on Big League Ball 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the runner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban! Get up! \NOn your feet, Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! I feel like\N I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Take 'em! Take 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take into account \Nyour running power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The flaw in my plan was my failing\N to consider the strain I placed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done it! \NHe's finally done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a monumental moment \Nfor Japanese baseball!{haven't quite got the  燦然と輝く  in, but ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Following on from Fujimoto, this is only the \Nsecond perfect game the Giants have ever had!{following on form Fujimoto?} {S: After Fujimoto, now also the Giants have achieved a perfect game!  // Fujimoto ni tsudzuite, Kyojin-gun futari mo no paafekuto tassei.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who has devoted his entire life to baseball has finally done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone with a small body, he's performed a massive feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the star!\N He truly is the star of the Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{don't suppose you can make this out? <_<} {S: nope, the beginning is too distorted, so making out the right word is kind of impossible for me lol} {imma assume this is a "maji ka yo"}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's Hoshi.\N - It's Coach Hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You put your life\N on the line and won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've truly\N surpassed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the winning ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, our father-son battle has finally come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been \Nsince you've called me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Hyuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,, I'm sure... to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been a\N real parent to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At least... at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me atone for my sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me carry you{on my back},\N just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I did when\N you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... thank you, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma, you put your life on the line and beat your father fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become a fine man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hyuuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the star you've been after this whole\N time is proof your life will start anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that the path\N ahead is treacherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know you'll conquer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前が野球と言う一つの人生の道場で栄光の星を手にしたぞ}That's right. You've finally obtained the star you've been longing for your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where life takes you, I know you'll do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Set your sights on a new star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Set your sights on a new star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}If you have it in you,\N head down the road of trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:06.48,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}And show them what men can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Burn bright like a true champion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}until the Star of the Giants\N is in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Go all out until you sweat blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Don't wipe away your tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:24.78,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Go, go, Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.98,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Head to your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:55.16,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}If you put your life on the line,\N you can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}With the discipline\N instilled by your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:09.07,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}a strong will to live,\N and a flaming-hot fastball,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.92,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}you press on until you \Nfulfill your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Go all out until you sweat blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.18,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Don't wipe away your tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:22.44,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Go, go, Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:26.79,Default,,0,260,0,,{\blur1.5\an9\fs45}Head to your future!
